Keith J. Allman 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer at MASCO CORP, Keith J. Allman  made $9,732,352 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,126,654 was received as a salary, $4,224,800 was received as a bonus, $1,327,054 was received in stock options, $2,442,825 was awarded as stock and $611,019 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


